      "comment": "LUST TO BURN (8) was a Other winner two back then out of the placings latest at this track but moves to Box 8 this time where she has performed well. Will find this more suitable and can atone. ROUGH GIRL MEL (2) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (17.88) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and six minor placings. Expected to be in this for a long way. LAP TO BURN (4) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Other winner three back (17.73) at this track over 305m. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Has the ability and can find best this time. KERRY'S CADILLAC (1) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
